    "ADAPTIVEHELM": "Adaptive Helm",
    "ITEM_ADAPTIVEHELM_NAME": "Adaptive Helm",
    "ITEM_ADAPTIVEHELM_PICKUP": "Gain defenses. Gain additional effects based on your character class.",
    "ITEM_ADAPTIVEHELM_DESC": "Gain <style=cEvent>{Common Stat Boost} armor</style> and a <style=cIsUtility>{Common Stat Boost}% max HP shield</style>. Gain additional effects based on your character's class.\n\n<style=cSub><u>Melee</u>:</style> Gain <style=cIsUtility>{Bonus Resist}%</style> <style=cStack>(+{Bonus Resist Extra Stacks}% per stack)</style> bonus <style=cEvent>armor</style> and <style=cIsUtility>shield</style>. When you take damage, reduce all <style=cWorldEvent>active cooldowns</style> by <style=cIsUtility>{Cooldown Refund} seconds</style>.\n<style=cSub><u>Ranged</u>:</style> Gain <style=cIsDamage>{Bonus Damage} <style=cStack>(+{Bonus Damage Extra Stacks} per stack)</style> BASE damage</style>. Refresh your <style=cWorldEvent>active cooldowns</style> every <style=cIsUtility>{Cooldown Interval} <style=cStack>(-{Cooldown Interval Reduction}% per stack)</style> seconds</style>.",
    "ITEM_ADAPTIVEHELM_LORE": "",
