    "ITEM_BLOODTHIRSTER_DESC": "Every <style=cIsUtility>{Effect Cooldown} seconds</style>, falling below <style=cIsHealth>{HP Threshold}% max HP</style> grants a <style=cHumanObjective>{Percent Barrier}% <style=cStack>(+{Percent Barrier Extra Stacks}% per stack)</style> max HP barrier</style>.",
