    "ITEM_GUINSOOSRAGEBLADE_DESC": "Gain a stack of <style=cWorldEvent>Wrath</style> for each consecutive hit against the same enemy. Stacks each grant <style=cIsDamage>{Attack Speed On-Hit}% <style=cStack>(+{Attack Speed On-Hit}% per stack)</style> attack speed</style> and are reset when hitting a new target.",
