    "ITEM_QUICKSILVER_PICKUP": "Upon activation of the teleporter, become <style=cWorldEvent>immune</style> to crowd control and periodically gain <style=cIsDamage>attack speed</style>.",
    "ITEM_QUICKSILVER_DESC": "Upon activation of the teleporter, become <style=cWorldEvent>immune</style> to crowd control for <style=cIsUtility>{CC Immunity Duration} <style=cStack>(+{CC Immunity Duration Extra Stacks} per stack)</style> seconds</style>. During this time, also gain <style=cIsDamage>{Attack Speed}% attack speed</style> per second.",
