    "ITEM_GAMBLERSBLADE_DESC": "Gain an additional <style=cIsDamage>0%</style>-<style=cIsDamage>{Attack Speed Effect Cap}% <style=cStack>(+{Attack Speed Effect Cap Extra Stacks}% per stack)</style> attack speed</style> based on your <style=cHumanObjective>current gold</style>, <style=cIsUtility>scaling with difficulty</style>. On-hit, <style=cIsUtility>{Drop Chance}%</style> chance to drop a treasure pickup worth <style=cHumanObjective>${Money Gain}</style>.",
