    "ITEM_STATIKKSHIV_DESC": "Every <style=cIsUtility>{Effect Cooldown} seconds</style>, your next hit chains up to {Number of Enemies Chained} enemies within <style=cIsUtility>{Zap Range}m</style>, dealing an additional <style=cIsDamage>{Bonus On-Hit}% <style=cStack>(+{Bonus On-Hit Per Stack}% per stack)</style> TOTAL damage</style> and applying <style=cWorldEvent>Sunder</style>, reducing armor by <style=cEvent>{Sunder Reduction}</style>.",
