    "SUNFIRECAPE": "Sunfire Cape",
    "ITEM_SUNFIRECAPE_NAME": "Sunfire Cape",
    "ITEM_SUNFIRECAPE_PICKUP": "<style=cEvent>+{Armor} armor</style>\n<style=cIsHealth>+{Flat Health}% max HP</style>\n\nGain <style=cIsHealth>{Percent Health}% max HP</style>. Every <style=cIsUtility>{Debuff Tick} seconds</style>, <style=cUserSetting>Burn</style> and <style=cDeath>Wound</style> nearby enemies.\n\n<style=cUserSetting>Burn</style>: Deal <style=cIsHealth>{Burn Per Second}% max HP</style> per second.\n<style=cDeath>Wound</style>: Reduces all <style=cIsHealing>healing and regneration</style> by <style=cDeath>{Wound Reduction}%</style> for <style=cIsUtility>{Wound Duration} seconds</style>.",
    "ITEM_SUNFIRECAPE_DESC": "<style=cEvent>+{Armor} armor</style>\n<style=cIsHealth>+{Flat Health}% max HP</style>\n\nGain <style=cIsHealth>{Percent Health}% max HP</style>. Every <style=cIsUtility>{Debuff Tick} seconds</style>, <style=cUserSetting>Burn</style> and <style=cDeath>Wound</style> nearby enemies.\n\n<style=cUserSetting>Burn</style>: Deal <style=cIsHealth>{Burn Per Second}% max HP</style> per second.\n<style=cDeath>Wound</style>: Reduces all <style=cIsHealing>healing and regneration</style> by <style=cDeath>{Wound Reduction}%</style> for <style=cIsUtility>{Wound Duration} seconds</style>.",
